36:22.447 --> 36:28.113
What I'm sayin' is, nobody's on your side!

36:29.087 --> 36:31.817
This is it, kids! Make it a good game!

36:34.993 --> 36:37.393
Nice speech old man.

36:37.495 --> 36:39.429
