42:03.454 --> 42:04.751
Where is it?

42:07.325 --> 42:08.189
Bingo!

42:11.930 --> 42:13.363
We're alive!

42:14.065 --> 42:14.929
Thank God!

42:15.033 --> 42:17.365
Seawater? Can't see shit.

42:18.970 --> 42:20.232
