42:20.338 --> 42:22.533
Smells fishy!

42:28.379 --> 42:29.573
Have no fear!

42:29.681 --> 42:34.584
Fear takes the shape we're willing to give it!

42:34.686 --> 42:37.917
Let's light a candle in our hearts,
make it gleam.

42:38.089 --> 42:39.818
Try to enjoy the moment!

42:40.391 --> 42:43.519
In spite of this turn of events.

42:44.562 --> 42:45.426
<i>"This is FUN"</i>

42:45.863 --> 42:49.026
This will shed a new light on things!

42:52.870 --> 42:55.361
Remember our days in grade school?

42:55.773 --> 43:00.972
When it was all play,
no restrictions or tomorrows?

43:01.613 --> 43:04.776
We didn't end up here 'cos we were chased!

43:05.049 --> 43:08.678
We came here seeking adventure!
An epic journey!

43:09.220 --> 43:11.085
Let the party begin!

43:15.059 --> 43:17.721
Hey, there's a boat!

43:20.765 --> 43:22.392
