46:23.981 --> 46:26.677
This place is dangerous, we need to move!

46:27.018 --> 46:28.576
Hurry! Hurry!

46:29.120 --> 46:33.557
- What the fuck?!
- C'mon, hurry!

46:39.430 --> 46:41.523
- What is this?
- An earthquake? A tsunami?

46:41.632 --> 46:45.966
- You guys are reckless!
- The fuck, old man?!

46:46.070 --> 46:51.337
Hurry up! Grab an ore and row!

46:53.544 --> 46:56.012
- Tidal wave?
- Tsunami!

46:58.049 --> 47:01.416
Move it, people!

47:03.855 --> 47:05.482
Over there!

47:05.590 --> 47:06.750
Almost there!

47:07.158 --> 47:09.524
Hang on!

47:29.146 --> 47:33.048
Meal time's over. We're OK now!

47:34.385 --> 47:35.852
Let's go up!

47:55.439 --> 47:59.500
