48:31.642 --> 48:33.940
Want to freshen up?

48:34.378 --> 48:38.508
Plenty of clean hot water?

48:38.616 --> 48:41.585
- You mean have a bath?
- Yes! Yes!

48:42.486 --> 48:43.817
I'd like that!

48:43.921 --> 48:46.549
Yeah? Me too!

49:00.671 --> 49:02.400
This is bliss!

49:04.742 --> 49:09.406
But boy we're in some mess! It's surreal!

49:10.314 --> 49:15.217
