50:14.078 --> 50:17.138
Those bastards! Not very subtle are they?!

50:17.248 --> 50:20.445
Let's pretend they're costumes!

50:20.551 --> 50:23.281
Hey, find something we can actually wear!

50:24.855 --> 50:27.016
Wow! Looks amazing!

50:28.325 --> 50:29.815
You made this?

50:30.227 --> 50:31.524
Gramps?

50:31.929 --> 50:33.521
Should've seen him at work!

50:33.631 --> 50:37.761
