50:37.868 --> 50:41.031
Where'd you learn to cook, gramps?

50:46.377 --> 50:48.572
Whoa!

50:51.782 --> 50:53.249
Yeah, it's delicious!

50:53.350 --> 50:54.977
5 stars in my book!

50:55.319 --> 50:57.583
Bon apetit!

50:59.557 --> 51:01.024
Wow.

51:01.125 --> 51:02.387
What a meal!

51:02.493 --> 51:03.926
Thanks!

51:04.028 --> 51:07.862
Much better than some fancy
rotating sushi bar in Kita.

51:08.866 --> 51:13.701
