Westernized sushi last year.

51:13.804 --> 51:15.567
Rotating sushi bars.

51:16.407 --> 51:19.001
Rotating sushi.

51:19.477 --> 51:21.672
Rotating sushi!

51:21.779 --> 51:23.838
Not like that!

51:25.116 --> 51:26.140
No, no.

51:26.250 --> 51:28.844
In front of the customers.

51:34.625 --> 51:37.116
Mine's dead too!

51:37.828 --> 51:39.796
It's a cell phone?

51:39.897 --> 51:43.458
A phone, a mobile phone?!

51:43.567 --> 51:45.535
I knew it!

51:46.170 --> 51:49.230
