store the other day!

52:06.157 --> 52:07.021
Yeah?

52:07.124 --> 52:10.958
Yes! I knew it!

52:14.532 --> 52:17.968
- How about flying cars?
- Huh?

52:19.803 --> 52:22.738
Hmm, how long have you been here exactly?

52:26.143 --> 52:29.579
More than 30 years!

52:31.882 --> 52:34.510
I had a big deal going down!

52:34.618 --> 52:38.019
Hid my stash in a comic book case!

52:42.193 --> 52:44.252
But I took the wrong one!

52:49.500 --> 52:53.334
Coastguards and DEA knew all about it anyway.

52:56.140 --> 53:00.008
Was running, lights flashing everywhere!

53:00.711 --> 53:05.978
When a huge whale swallowed me!

53:06.450 --> 53:07.974
Couldn't believe it.

53:12.523 --> 53:13.888
And then what?

53:14.058 --> 53:17.289
Got caught in the waves!

53:17.995 --> 53:20.896
It was pitch dark when I came around!

53:21.699 --> 53:25.226
Tried to escape but the waves were too rough!

53:25.970 --> 53:28.666
<i>"TIME BOY"
Tried again! And again.</i>

53:30.507 --> 53:35.877
I couldn't have survived without my friends.

53:38.749 --> 53:40.683
Um, where's the toilet?

53:40.784 --> 53:45.187
The washroom? Straight ahead! I'll take you!

53:45.289 --> 53:49.157
Nah, it's okay! Straight ahead, right?

53:56.433 --> 53:57.764
Oh my God!

54:13.217 --> 54:15.117
Hey, keep talking!

54:19.623 --> 54:23.115
- Where's the "exit?"
- All the way down there!

54:23.827 --> 54:25.920
- Oh, right!
- But of course!

54:26.630 --> 54:28.120
