54:28.432 --> 54:32.562
Got to know your own limits!

54:51.555 --> 54:53.318
We're outta here!

54:55.993 --> 54:57.517
We can go this way.

54:59.096 --> 55:01.496
It's wobbling!

55:01.865 --> 55:03.992
It's the only way, c'mon!

55:06.770 --> 55:08.499
It'll be alright!

55:12.242 --> 55:15.040
You'll get killed!

55:15.312 --> 55:17.576
He's hungry again!

55:17.948 --> 55:18.915
Hurry!

55:19.016 --> 55:20.881
Come back!

55:20.984 --> 55:22.417
Wait!

55:22.619 --> 55:25.281
- The water's coming!
- Nishi!

55:28.759 --> 55:30.784
