56:47.638 --> 56:49.902
<i>And a "Happy Mornin'" to y'all!</i>

56:50.007 --> 56:51.998
<i>Wow, is this a beautiful day or what?</i>

56:52.109 --> 56:57.672
<i>You wouldn't believe how blue the sky was
this morning.</i>

56:57.781 --> 56:59.681
In line with the solar system!

56:59.783 --> 57:04.243
Thought I'd drive
all the way to Brazil, y'know?

57:04.354 --> 57:07.687
<i>Well, it's gonna be booming
at the resorts today!</i>

57:07.791 --> 57:13.730
