or work, I tell ya!</i>

57:17.134 --> 57:21.798
Now, now, now!

57:22.105 --> 57:24.835
C'mon, cheer up!

57:24.942 --> 57:30.710
You're homesick, I've been there.
I cried and got angry too.

57:30.814 --> 57:33.749
But I realized after coming here!

57:33.851 --> 57:36.581
Oh, whatever!

57:36.820 --> 57:40.017
Got an idea! There's a place
that'll cheer you up.

57:40.123 --> 57:41.784
Great friends too!

57:41.892 --> 57:44.122
Let's go! Everybody!

57:46.363 --> 57:48.092
<i>So wrecked cars are popping up everywhere!</i>

57:48.198 --> 57:51.258
<i>Must've been some monster car chase!</i>

57:51.735 --> 57:54.602
You haven't eaten properly in 3 days!

57:54.705 --> 57:56.798
You're not gonna last that way!

57:56.907 --> 57:59.842
