57:59.943 --> 58:02.878
And Nishi, you've eaten nothing!

58:02.980 --> 58:04.971
Forget about getting it up!

58:06.884 --> 58:08.078
Hey!

58:09.353 --> 58:10.752
Just shut up, okay?

58:28.238 --> 58:32.868
Gramps, will you take me to that fun place
