58:33.277 --> 58:35.745
Wanna go? It'll be fun!

58:36.013 --> 58:37.071
I need a change!

58:37.180 --> 58:40.946
That's the spirit! You'll love it!

58:41.051 --> 58:43.110
Nishi?

58:43.220 --> 58:44.653
You too!

58:45.756 --> 58:48.316
Nah! Count me out!

58:48.425 --> 58:51.417
It'll be fun! You can meet my friends too!

58:51.528 --> 58:54.190
Hearts'll sore! Heads'll explode!

58:54.331 --> 58:57.732
Cut it, Gramps! I'm not in the mood!

58:57.834 --> 58:59.529
Just leave me alone!

59:02.005 --> 59:04.735
Join us later if you feel like it, okay?

59:04.841 --> 59:06.502
Let's go, Myon.

59:06.810 --> 59:08.744
Let's go, let's go!

59:09.046 --> 59:10.707
