59:57.394 --> 59:58.452
Asshole!

59:58.562 --> 01:00:00.052
Loser!

01:00:18.382 --> 01:00:21.374
<i>"Help me God I'm sorry"</i>

01:00:26.757 --> 01:00:29.749
