01:01:45.769 --> 01:01:48.169
<i>Gotta drink your milk, honey!</i>

01:02:03.854 --> 01:02:04.718
<i>30 years!</i>

01:02:32.816 --> 01:02:33.748
You okay?

01:02:33.850 --> 01:02:36.614
Isn't it amazing, Nishi?

01:02:41.792 --> 01:02:44.192
Gramps, I...

