01:03:11.555 --> 01:03:14.683
But I managed to survive!

01:03:15.292 --> 01:03:17.260
I can swim again!

01:03:17.360 --> 01:03:22.127
Catch things, walk, see.

01:03:22.666 --> 01:03:24.429
Isn't that fun?

01:03:24.534 --> 01:03:30.666
Seawater's salty! This place stinks!
But it gives me joy!

01:03:30.774 --> 01:03:36.110
Would you rather lie around doing nothing?
Or would you rather feel alive?

01:03:36.479 --> 01:03:39.073
Which is more fun?

01:06:07.197 --> 01:06:08.687
She sure can swim!

